Find systems with test results above the EPA standard¶

Which water systems had at least one result above the EPA standard of 15 parts per billion? In which years? What percentage of water systems had a test over the threshold?

In [37]:
EPA_THRESHOLD = 15

max_results = df.groupby(['PWSID', df.COLLECTION_DATE.dt.year])['RESULT'].max()
max_results[max_results > EPA_THRESHOLD].unstack().head()

In [33]:
import folium
from folium import features

def make_map(df, value_col=None, label='PWSNAME', zoom_start=7):
    df = df[df['lat'].notnull()]
    center = [df['lat'].mean(), df['lng'].mean()]
    max_radius = 10000
    if value_col:
        max_value = df[value_col].max()
        
    m = folium.Map(location=center, zoom_start=zoom_start)
    
    for i, row in df.iterrows():
        if value_col is None:
            features.Marker(location=[row['lat'], row['lng']], popup=row[label]).add_to(m)
        else:
            features.CircleMarker(location=[row['lat'], row['lng']],
                    radius=row[value_col] / max_value * max_radius,
                    popup=row[label], color='#3186cc',
                    fill_color='#3186cc').add_to(m)
    
    m.save('map.html')
    return m
